Class RegistrationManager

java.lang.Object
RegistrationManager
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.io.Serializable
public class RegistrationManager
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable
Represents a course Registration Manager that process the logic and flow of course registration. Registration Manager is a Control Class.
